      "message": "For consistency, there should also be a change to _notify_container() in k8splugin/tasks.py, starting at line 680.  The code in _notify_container is setting up a script that's executed in a container to notify the container of a policy change.   It will also have a problem if the script definition includes an argument list.  The change there is somewhat more involved than the change here.",
